\begin{frame}{Aim of the project}
The aim of this project consisted in a multitemporal analysis of the vegetation state based on the changes over time of the following parameters:
\smallskip
    \begin{itemize} 
    \item \textbf{Fraction of Green Vegetation Cover} (FCover)\\
    corresponds to the fraction of ground covered by green vegetation.
    %it quantifies the spatial extent of the vegetation
    \item \textbf{Normalized Difference Vegetation Index} (NDVI)\\
    is an indicator of the greenness of the biomes.
    \begin{equation}
          NDVI=\frac{NIR-RED}{NIR+RED}
          %REF_nir and REF_red are the spectral reflectances measured in the near infrared and red wavebands respectively
    \end{equation}
    where:\\
    $NIR$ = reflectance in the near-infrared band\\
    $R$ = reflectance in the red band.
\end{itemize}
\end{frame}
}

